++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
                         PRESENCE SENSE
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

	Level: 3
	Cost: 35
	Text: sense invisible

	A psionicist can reach out with his mind to feel the presence
        of others in a room. With this power you will be able to tell
        if there are any invisible people in the room with you.

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
